        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Carina Heights property values vary by block size, position and condition. Its elevated position with views across the eastern suburbs, combined with larger block sizes, attracts buyers seeking more space than Coorparoo or Camp Hill typically offer at similar price points.</p>
