          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Carina Heights has a mix of post-war homes, brick houses from the 1970s and 1980s, and a growing number of renovated properties that have taken advantage of the suburb's elevated topography and city views. The block sizes tend to be generous by inner-east standards.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
